- Eu fiz alguns contatos.

447
00:35:22,100 --> 00:35:23,800
Arranjou algum nome?

448
00:35:24,700 --> 00:35:26,400
Sim, arranjei.

449
00:35:26,500 --> 00:35:28,300
O Grande Danton.

